WEBVTT

00:06:27.762 --> 00:06:31.689
Bizda har kunlik badbo'y kiyim va 
yoqimsiz taom bor.

00:06:32.464 --> 00:06:34.501
Shu bilan birga ulkan muammolarimiz bor:

00:06:34.525 --> 00:06:37.826
kassaliklar, atrof muhit ifloslanishi 
va urushlar.

00:06:39.326 --> 00:06:41.010
Shuning uchun mening vazifam
nafaqat

00:06:41.034 --> 00:06:44.264
atrofimizdagi mikroskopik hayotni katalog
qilishdan iborat

00:06:44.288 --> 00:06:47.537
balkim bizga aynan nima yordam bera
olishini aniqlashdir.

00:06:48.681 --> 00:06:50.046
Sizlarga bir misol aytaman.

00:06:50.070 --> 00:06:51.702
Biz zararkunanda va

00:06:51.726 --> 00:06:54.074
uyimizda uchraydigan ko'plab 
arilardan boshladik.

00:06:54.707 --> 00:06:59.634
Arining ichida hali to'liq o'rganilmagan 
noyob qobiliyatga ega bo'lgan pivo

00:06:59.658 --> 00:07:01.047
tayyorlay oladigan mikro-